{"tid":922493,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪為男友學廚獲讚","createTime":"2018-11-30T11:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T10:49:25.000Z","uid":9573,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"180cee4ba32578c3ae6845ea78246aabda3779d2","tid":922493,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T11:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181125/large/25ec3p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181125%2Flarge%2F25ec3p1.jpg&h=50ec1be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱千雪和「蜘蛛女」鄭麗莎昨日在將軍澳出席聖誕節揭幕活動，即場學煮新加坡美食，她說：「第一次煮，平時一年都會煮一、兩次，因為有時諗唔到送乜生日禮物畀男朋友、朋友，咁我就會煮，我上網學煮糖醋排骨，男友食過，佢話OK就當係拿手，因為男友煮嘢食好叻，我冇諗過同佢比。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoPpFYD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoPpFYD.gif&h=40542cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時修讀法律系的朱千雪表示，下月初要考試至聖誕前夕：「如果考得好就放假，考得唔好就要準備補考。」她透露還有一年就畢業。對於有報道指朱千雪未畢業就獲一間律師行聘用，美匯指數受此拖累進一步下跌至96.60，她未有正面回答，只道：「我目標係畢咗業先，完成咗先搵工做。」"},{"pid":"0d3df8024f9f52bf4fd1955a1b3279bda3f99337","tid":922493,"uid":106426,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"170a21759b7ca3cc3c1056997ce69e9bc6e2c6f2","tid":922493,"uid":65598,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0d3df8024f9f52bf4fd1955a1b3279bda3f99337","tid":922493,"uid":106426,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T11:56:37.000Z","msg":"咪撚痴線啦"},{"pid":"cc93abbabf078afcfd4cd9f50de8fcff63998198","tid":922493,"uid":38904,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"0d3df8024f9f52bf4fd1955a1b3279bda3f99337","tid":922493,"uid":106426,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://